326ea17e474e669602fc7fcbfa2d9d05b62a6307a6c999f311832702096fad4ad5bfc112649747f5dacf9753b913eed741209eff9d8d9fbeae76f3ecb5636d49  0001-kalarm-Add-search-ktextwidgets.patch
"
